  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objectives of this 12-week study are to evaluate the efficacy, safety, and tolerability
      of AVP-786 as an adjunctive treatment compared with placebo in patients with residual
      schizophrenia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
